  <brief_title>Tolerability and Measurability of the Efficacy of Non Pharmaceutical Measures to Prevent Seasonal Influenza</brief_title>
  <official_title>Tolerability and Measurability of the Efficacy of Non Pharmaceutical Measures to Prevent Seasonal Influenza</official_title>
