  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  influenza like illness symptoms

          -  positive rapid test for influenza

          -  inclusion within 48h of symptom onset

          -  inclusion of at least 3 members of a household (including index case)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe illness

          -  other cases of similar symptoms within 14 days before onset of symptoms in index
             patient

          -  severe asthma or COPD

          -  pregnancy of index
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
